Preamble: My Vasundhara Abhiyan 4. The procedure for the award of cash prizes to the winning local bodies in the 12 categories of the award has been notified vide Government Decision dated 27.09.2024 at Reference No. (1). Accordingly, a Detailed Project Report of the works to be taken up by the local bodies out of the award amount has been prepared vide Government Decision dated 08.02.2022 at Reference No. Administrative approval has to be obtained from a committee constituted under the chairmanship of Secretary, Department of Environment and Climate Change.

2. Accordingly, for grant of administrative approval to the Detailed Project Report received from the Awardee Local Bodies, Ms. The Committee has made recommendations after discussing the Detailed Project Report submitted by the Local Bodies in its meetings held on 26th August 2025 under the chairmanship of Secretary, Department of Environment & Climate Change. It was under the consideration of the government to grant administrative approval to the Detailed Project Report of the respective local bodies as recommended by the committee.

Government Decision: Considering the points mentioned in the Preamble, the total amount received by Kanhewadi Gram Panchayat under Maji Vasundhara Abhiyan 4.0 is Rs. 50.00 The focus will be on the works to be undertaken out of the prize money of Rs. The Detailed Project Report costing ₹50,00, 000.00 (Rupees fifty lakhs only) has been submitted by the Village Development Officer, Kanhewadi Gram Panchayat with the technical approval of the Executive Engineer, Zilla Parishad Pune. The proposal was submitted by the Kanhewadi Gram Panchayat. The committee constituted under the chairmanship of Secretary, Department of Environment and Climate Change was constituted on 26th August, 2025.
Government Decision No: MAWA-0825 / P.No.159 (48) / T. A. 1.

was considered. As per the recommendation made by the said Committee, the total amount submitted by HAS Gram Panchayat is Rs. The works in the Detailed Project Report costing ₹50,00, 000.00 (Rupees fifty lakhs only) are being accorded administrative sanction by the Government subject to the following conditions and conditions. The works for which administrative sanction is being granted are shown in the accompanying Annexure-9.
2. Terms and Conditions 1) The working mechanism for the works in this Detailed Project Report shall be the Kanhewadi Gram Panchayat.

2) The financial and physical progress report of the implementation of the works mentioned in this Detailed Project Report should be sent to my Vasundhara Mission Directorate by the 5th of every month.
3) The implementation of the works in this Detailed Project Report should be completed within the next 6 months from the date of administrative approval.
4) Expenditure in excess of the prize money should be made out of self-funding.
5) In case of any increase in the original project cost in this Detailed Project Report for any reason, no additional funds / grants will be made available for the same.
